      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOYARRA KONGK (2) missed the frame latest (25.47) when fourth over 450m at this track in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw. Rates a leading player. UTAH ICON (8) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 25.65 beating Sunny Stride. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Significant danger. BIG BOY CABANG (4) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind How Amazing (25.56) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. The form from his last run stacks up well. Expecting another good run. STRUCK THE LOT (1) looks an each-way chance.",
